<item>
            <title>[LU-5769] lustre-rsync-test test_3b: writemany failed: No space left on device</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5769</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Li Wei &amp;lt;liwei@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/0e696d26-56cc-11e4-851f-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/0e696d26-56cc-11e4-851f-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_3b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;writemany failed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== lustre-rsync-test test 3b: Replicate files created by writemany == 10:17:32 (1413627452)
CMD: shadow-19vm8 lctl --device lustre-MDT0000 changelog_register -n
lustre-MDT0000: Registered changelog user cl7
CMD: shadow-19vm8 lctl get_param -n mdd.lustre-MDT0000.changelog_users
writemany-3: 1413627505.319899 error: open(/mnt/lustre/d3b.lustre-rsync-test/f3b.lustre-rsync-test-3-2758): No space left on device
writemany: error: PID 2901 had rc=28
 lustre-rsync-test test_3b: @@@@@@ FAIL: writemany failed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: lustre-rsync-test 3b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
